<break time="2.5s"/>

Wiggle your fingers gently.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Notice how they feel different now.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Filled with warmth.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Filled with purpose.
<break time="2.5s"/>

Take a deeper breath.
<break time="2s"/>
Feel energy returning to your body.
<break time="2s"/>

One.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Beginning to awaken.
<break time="1.2s"/>

Two.
<break time="1.2s"/>
More aware of your surroundings.
<break time="1.2s"/>

Three.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Feeling refreshed, renewed, transformed.
<break time="1.5s"/>

</prosody>

